This is the Debian GNU prepackaged version of Gawk, a pattern
scanning and processing language.  Gawk was <s>written by Diane Barlow
Close, Arnold D. Robbins, Paul H. Rubin and Richard Stallman.</s>

This package was <s>put together by Chris Fearnley <cjf@netaxs.com></s> (debian.*
files were originally prepared by Ian Murdock <imurdock@debian.org>),
from sources obtained from:

ftp://ftp.gnu.org/pub/gnu/gawk/gawk-3.1.5.tar.gz

It is currently being <s>maintained by James Troup <james@nocrew.org>.</s>

